  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A student who was dragged to Kadalalai",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Three university students who were taking a bath in the natural swimming pool of Gandhara-Sittagala were swept away by the sea waves, while one went missing.",
        "A 22-year-old first-year student at Ruhunu University's Faculty of Technology has gone missing.",
        "A group of 17 students were taking a bath in the lagoon when three students were swept away by a sudden surge in the sea.",
        "However, it has been reported that two students were rescued and are undergoing treatment at Matara Hospital.",
        "The residents of the area and the Gandhara police have jointly launched a search operation for the missing student."
      ],
